{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/blog/birdwatch","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<br>\n<h1>Introduction</h1>\n<p>People come to Twitter to stay informed, and they want credible information to help them do so. This isn’t always easy with the spread of misleading information online. Birdwatch is a community-driven approach to addressing this problem, seeking to create a better-informed world.</p>\n<h1>Project journal</h1>\n<p>Currently, Birdwatch is in pilot mode for people in the US. We’re building it in the open, with the public’s input, and we’re taking significant steps to make Birdwatch transparent. In the spirit of building in public, I decided to keep a journal of learnings, launches and changes.</p>\n<h1>October 21 2020</h1>\n<p>I joined the team!</p>\n<p>The product was in shaping stage. My main goals during this time were to work with our researcher to identify main pain points with our prototype and prepare the product for launch date, while working with our product lead to define the roadmap post-launch.</p>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"birdwatch add a note\"\n        title=\"birdwatch add a note\"\n        src=\"/static/674493c101b6a2a2e31d7fa43b908f7f/d61c2/birdwatch-add-a-note.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/674493c101b6a2a2e31d7fa43b908f7f/fc2a6/birdwatch-add-a-note.png 450w,\n/static/674493c101b6a2a2e31d7fa43b908f7f/1cfc2/birdwatch-add-a-note.png 900w,\n/static/674493c101b6a2a2e31d7fa43b908f7f/d61c2/birdwatch-add-a-note.png 1800w,\n/static/674493c101b6a2a2e31d7fa43b908f7f/b2313/birdwatch-add-a-note.png 2700w,\n/static/674493c101b6a2a2e31d7fa43b908f7f/75ac7/birdwatch-add-a-note.png 3600w,\n/static/674493c101b6a2a2e31d7fa43b908f7f/e6283/birdwatch-add-a-note.png 4096w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<h1>Jan 25 2021</h1>\n<p>Our pilot program <a href=\"https://twitter.com/birdwatch/status/1353774171684106243\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">launched</a>, allowing a groups of people to add notes to Tweets they think could be misleading, and rate the quality of each others’ notes.</p>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"birdwatch data\"\n        title=\"birdwatch data\"\n        src=\"/static/456d5e9d9e36e88ee77e57fe6ed2d4a3/d61c2/birdwatch-data.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/456d5e9d9e36e88ee77e57fe6ed2d4a3/fc2a6/birdwatch-data.png 450w,\n/static/456d5e9d9e36e88ee77e57fe6ed2d4a3/1cfc2/birdwatch-data.png 900w,\n/static/456d5e9d9e36e88ee77e57fe6ed2d4a3/d61c2/birdwatch-data.png 1800w,\n/static/456d5e9d9e36e88ee77e57fe6ed2d4a3/b2313/birdwatch-data.png 2700w,\n/static/456d5e9d9e36e88ee77e57fe6ed2d4a3/75ac7/birdwatch-data.png 3600w,\n/static/456d5e9d9e36e88ee77e57fe6ed2d4a3/e6283/birdwatch-data.png 4096w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<h1>Feb 01 2021</h1>\n<p>Released our first Birdwatch dataset. We publish data daily so that anyone — experts, academics, reporters, hobbyists — has free access to audit, identify problems, and spot opportunities to make Birdwatch better.</p>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"birdwatch tabs\"\n        title=\"birdwatch tabs\"\n        src=\"/static/ab9a9de1afa8c55253aa754af879a6a6/d61c2/birdwatch-tabs.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ab9a9de1afa8c55253aa754af879a6a6/fc2a6/birdwatch-tabs.png 450w,\n/static/ab9a9de1afa8c55253aa754af879a6a6/1cfc2/birdwatch-tabs.png 900w,\n/static/ab9a9de1afa8c55253aa754af879a6a6/d61c2/birdwatch-tabs.png 1800w,\n/static/ab9a9de1afa8c55253aa754af879a6a6/b2313/birdwatch-tabs.png 2700w,\n/static/ab9a9de1afa8c55253aa754af879a6a6/75ac7/birdwatch-tabs.png 3600w,\n/static/ab9a9de1afa8c55253aa754af879a6a6/e6283/birdwatch-tabs.png 4096w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<h1>Feb 17 2021</h1>\n<p>Introduced two different tabs in our main page with the goal of elevating helpful content.</p>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"birdwatch notification 2\"\n        title=\"birdwatch notification 2\"\n        src=\"/static/d1521cf799abda06bb9ae7243f5495b7/d61c2/birdwatch-notification-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d1521cf799abda06bb9ae7243f5495b7/fc2a6/birdwatch-notification-2.png 450w,\n/static/d1521cf799abda06bb9ae7243f5495b7/1cfc2/birdwatch-notification-2.png 900w,\n/static/d1521cf799abda06bb9ae7243f5495b7/d61c2/birdwatch-notification-2.png 1800w,\n/static/d1521cf799abda06bb9ae7243f5495b7/b2313/birdwatch-notification-2.png 2700w,\n/static/d1521cf799abda06bb9ae7243f5495b7/75ac7/birdwatch-notification-2.png 3600w,\n/static/d1521cf799abda06bb9ae7243f5495b7/e6283/birdwatch-notification-2.png 4096w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<h1>Mar 01 2021</h1>\n<p>Introduced our first notification in order to provide incentives and reminders to contributors</p>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"birdwatch note component\"\n        title=\"birdwatch note component\"\n        src=\"/static/263ed7030c58cdc7ad6da248b902a7af/d61c2/birdwatch-note-component.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/263ed7030c58cdc7ad6da248b902a7af/fc2a6/birdwatch-note-component.png 450w,\n/static/263ed7030c58cdc7ad6da248b902a7af/1cfc2/birdwatch-note-component.png 900w,\n/static/263ed7030c58cdc7ad6da248b902a7af/d61c2/birdwatch-note-component.png 1800w,\n/static/263ed7030c58cdc7ad6da248b902a7af/b2313/birdwatch-note-component.png 2700w,\n/static/263ed7030c58cdc7ad6da248b902a7af/75ac7/birdwatch-note-component.png 3600w,\n/static/263ed7030c58cdc7ad6da248b902a7af/e6283/birdwatch-note-component.png 4096w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<h1>Mar 19 2021</h1>\n<p>From a first-principles decision that quality of content on Birdwatch should be more important than who wrote it, we hid author’s name from the note component. This change also helps keep our contributors safe.</p>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"birdwatch menu\"\n        title=\"birdwatch menu\"\n        src=\"/static/8e2712e701882aebb64da74dd5c6e737/d61c2/birdwatch-menu.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8e2712e701882aebb64da74dd5c6e737/fc2a6/birdwatch-menu.png 450w,\n/static/8e2712e701882aebb64da74dd5c6e737/1cfc2/birdwatch-menu.png 900w,\n/static/8e2712e701882aebb64da74dd5c6e737/d61c2/birdwatch-menu.png 1800w,\n/static/8e2712e701882aebb64da74dd5c6e737/b2313/birdwatch-menu.png 2700w,\n/static/8e2712e701882aebb64da74dd5c6e737/75ac7/birdwatch-menu.png 3600w,\n/static/8e2712e701882aebb64da74dd5c6e737/e6283/birdwatch-menu.png 4096w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<h1>Apr 02 2021</h1>\n<p>Birdwatch becomes a first-class citizen on the Twitter menu, giving contributors a more convenient way to access the platform.</p>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"birdwatch nudge\"\n        title=\"birdwatch nudge\"\n        src=\"/static/8db05cebbd4b51a8fd5d52a930ffa761/d61c2/birdwatch-nudge.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8db05cebbd4b51a8fd5d52a930ffa761/fc2a6/birdwatch-nudge.png 450w,\n/static/8db05cebbd4b51a8fd5d52a930ffa761/1cfc2/birdwatch-nudge.png 900w,\n/static/8db05cebbd4b51a8fd5d52a930ffa761/d61c2/birdwatch-nudge.png 1800w,\n/static/8db05cebbd4b51a8fd5d52a930ffa761/b2313/birdwatch-nudge.png 2700w,\n/static/8db05cebbd4b51a8fd5d52a930ffa761/75ac7/birdwatch-nudge.png 3600w,\n/static/8db05cebbd4b51a8fd5d52a930ffa761/e6283/birdwatch-nudge.png 4096w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<h1>Apr 15 2021</h1>\n<p>Introduced simple nudges that guide people to writing more helpful notes. For example, reminding them to add sources or explain why they think a Tweet is misleading.</p>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"birdwatch notification C\"\n        title=\"birdwatch notification C\"\n        src=\"/static/1acc347dc8f199c31e50b50edc429907/d61c2/birdwatch-notification-C.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1acc347dc8f199c31e50b50edc429907/fc2a6/birdwatch-notification-C.png 450w,\n/static/1acc347dc8f199c31e50b50edc429907/1cfc2/birdwatch-notification-C.png 900w,\n/static/1acc347dc8f199c31e50b50edc429907/d61c2/birdwatch-notification-C.png 1800w,\n/static/1acc347dc8f199c31e50b50edc429907/b2313/birdwatch-notification-C.png 2700w,\n/static/1acc347dc8f199c31e50b50edc429907/75ac7/birdwatch-notification-C.png 3600w,\n/static/1acc347dc8f199c31e50b50edc429907/e6283/birdwatch-notification-C.png 4096w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<h1>Apr 29 2021</h1>\n<p>Introduced notifications to reward helpful raters, as well as writers.</p>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"birdwatch pivots\"\n        title=\"birdwatch pivots\"\n        src=\"/static/f043dac8fd5cbd82f16ddf180e6f02fa/d61c2/birdwatch-pivots.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f043dac8fd5cbd82f16ddf180e6f02fa/fc2a6/birdwatch-pivots.png 450w,\n/static/f043dac8fd5cbd82f16ddf180e6f02fa/1cfc2/birdwatch-pivots.png 900w,\n/static/f043dac8fd5cbd82f16ddf180e6f02fa/d61c2/birdwatch-pivots.png 1800w,\n/static/f043dac8fd5cbd82f16ddf180e6f02fa/b2313/birdwatch-pivots.png 2700w,\n/static/f043dac8fd5cbd82f16ddf180e6f02fa/75ac7/birdwatch-pivots.png 3600w,\n/static/f043dac8fd5cbd82f16ddf180e6f02fa/e6283/birdwatch-pivots.png 4096w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<h1>Jun 2 2021</h1>\n<p>Birdwatch notes started appearing on Twitter, for pilot participants only. It’s a big milestone because it means contributors can get a better sense of the “whole cycle” of their contributions and impact.</p>\n<div class=\"w-100 tc mb4\">\n  <video class=\"w-100 br2\" autoplay loop muted>\n  <source src=\"/194da8c3dedd0f23ee87b41f1cf0bad2/birdwatch-guide.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n  </video>\n</div>\n<h1>Jun 14 2021</h1>\n<p>Launched a reputation system that ranks contributors according to how helpful they are. We also <a href=\"https://twitter.github.io/birdwatch/about/ranking-notes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">published</a> the code that powers this system in the open-source community, on a Github Pages Hugo website I built and help maintain.</p>\n<h1>Stay tuned for more!</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/birdwatch\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"bg-white ba link pa3 ph4 br-pill fw6 bg-hover-near-white\" style=\"\">Follow us @Birdwatch</a></p>","frontmatter":{"date":"January 25, 2021","path":"/blog/birdwatch","title":"Twitter Birdwatch","topics":["product design"],"subtitle":"A community-driven solution to misleading information","problem":"The spread of online misinformation is too large to tackle with centralized tools.","solution":"Empower users to add and moderate context around misleading Tweets.","impact":"Currently in pilot mode, results will be shared publicly as we iterate.","color":"#6BC9FB","where":null,"learn_more":null,"learnings":null,"team":["Twitter Inc"],"myrole":"Design Lead","link":"http://twitter.github.io/birdwatch","link_label":"Birdwatch Guide","cover_image":{"publicURL":"/static/019703952192527a6a771128cb2a5faf/birdwatch-hero.png","childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":0.9668508287292817,"src":"/static/019703952192527a6a771128cb2a5faf/73c85/birdwatch-hero.png","srcSet":"/static/019703952192527a6a771128cb2a5faf/d4144/birdwatch-hero.png 175w,\n/static/019703952192527a6a771128cb2a5faf/a5370/birdwatch-hero.png 350w,\n/static/019703952192527a6a771128cb2a5faf/73c85/birdwatch-hero.png 700w,\n/static/019703952192527a6a771128cb2a5faf/4ff95/birdwatch-hero.png 1050w,\n/static/019703952192527a6a771128cb2a5faf/54967/birdwatch-hero.png 1400w,\n/static/019703952192527a6a771128cb2a5faf/2ef01/birdwatch-hero.png 3960w","sizes":"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"prev":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/blog/petal-before-and-after","title":"Everyday quick-wins","subtitle":"A journal of small steps towards simplicity and meaning.","cover":true,"color":"#f7bcbc","cover_image":{"publicURL":"/static/42f39593a7f582ca66cd6d32708a08f8/petal-phone-hero-2.png"}}},"next":null}}}